{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban the purchase & delivery of alcohol via delivery apps",
        "additional_details": "We believe that alcohol should only be sold through licensed premises with in-person age verification. The Government should pass legislation to implement this ban and work with local authorities and licensing bodies to prevent alcohol purchases, sales and delivery via delivery apps.",
        "background": "Ban the purchase, sale and delivery of alcohol via delivery apps to protect vulnerable and people who are underage.",
